✅ 5) Remote Repositories (GitHub)

Q44. What is remote repository?

✅ Answer:
Remote repo is a repo stored online (GitHub/GitLab) used for collaboration.

Q45. Connect local repo to remote
git remote add origin <repo-url>

Check:
git remote -v

Q46. Push and Pull

Push
git push origin main

Pull
git pull origin main

📌 Push vs Pull:

push → local to remote
pull → remote to local

Q47. Clone a repo
git clone <repo-url>

