✅ 6) Pull Requests (PR) (Must for QC)

Q48. What is a Pull Request?

✅ Answer (Winning):
A Pull Request is a request to merge code changes from one branch into another (example: feature → main) after review.

📌 Why PR?

code review
avoid bugs
maintain quality
team collaboration

Q49. PR workflow (Simple)

✅ Steps:

create branch
commit changes
push branch
create PR
review + approve
merge

